comments: While in a legal defensive position, Randle (NYK) makes marginal contact with Embiid (PHI), but the contact does not cause Embiid to lose position of the ball.
Randle (NYK) makes incidental contact with Embiid (PHI) while making a play on the ball.
Harris (PHI) is retreating and makes marginal contact with Morris Sr. (NYK) on his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Robinson (NYK) establishes himself in a legal picking position in the path of Harris (PHI).
Harris (PHI) maintains a legal guarding position during Morris Sr.'s (NYK) driving shot attempt.
After Embiid's (PHI) shot attempt, Scott (PHI) extends his forearm into Ntilikina (PHI) body, dislodging him from his legally obtained position.
Ntilikina (NYK) makes hand on ball on contact prior to Harris' (NYK) pass.
Barrett (NYK) makes clean contact to the ball on the catch by Embiid (PHI).
Simmons (PHI) trips Morris Sr. (NYK) in the back-court.
Dotson (NYK) makes contact to Burke's (PHI) body on the drive that affects his SQBR.
Prior to the inbound, Randle (NYK) sets the screen and delivers contact to Thybulle (PHI).
Embiid (PHI) sets the screen on Barrett (NYK) and the two make incidental contact with one another as they disengage.
Barrett (NYK) commits a take foul on Burke (PHI).
Randle (NYK) establishes himself in a legal screening position in the path of Burke (PHI).
Ntilikina (NYK) commits a take foul on Thybulle (PHI).
Dotson (NYK) commits a take foul on Embiid (PHI).
